column5: How was the fishing up at Lake Ramsey this past year? I was planning a trip up there June 2001.

We went to Ramsey Lake for the first time last year (2nd week of June) and had a good time. I had one day where I caught 22 walleyes myself. The largest one we caught was 27.5"Russ>How was the fishing up at >Lake Ramsey this past year? >I was planning a trip >up there June 2001.
